        <td width="500" height="18" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#993333" class="box_titles">Finally an update! <span class="box_titles_small">March 27, 2005, 11:10:59 PM by <a href="mailto:noah@uberyou.com">Noah</a></span>		</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td width="763" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#996666" class="box_links">
		So there isn't much to update.  We raid each day and collect the loot that doesn't seem to improve all that much.  When you can walk up to Darathar with 13 people (17 actually but 1 was a bot and 3 were afk scouts) and beat the shit out of him w/o one casualty, things start to get older than re-runs of Seinfeld.  By no means does this mean we won't pharm whenever but at this point in EQ2 there is no huge pressure to gear everyone up in full raid loot for bigger power pools, hps, or dps.  Nothing remotely challenges us.  Sure it is nice to get some gear and metal boxes but we are not much for rubbing off to uber loot stats (since we already have most everything in the game).  All we can hope for is a mighty expansion that will once again bring the pain of being in debt and facing mobs that making you hold your breath, and not your dick, the entire fight.<br /><br />   Speaking of expansions.  The little adventure pack kept some of us busy for a few days but soon enough our boys here stood up and took the server 1st on the boss, another for the record books.<br /><br /><br /><A HREF="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10092/normal_EQ2_000016.jpg"><img src=http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10092/normal_EQ2_000016.jpg border=0 width=700 height=525></A></center><br /><br /><br />Excuse the fucking white blob... leet strat bubble txt is how we win.  The fight was more challenging than anything in the game at the moment.  As you can see it was sweet to have the server 1st broadcast to everyone (nice touch devs).  One thing I need to find out is who would even THINK of a particle effect of purple smoke exhailing from the face?  Someone was smoking something when they decided this would be a good idea.<br /><br />   Thanks for the "raid" zone! A few encounters brought our priests back from AFK.  Still, raid mobs are just not configured right yet.  30 raid mobs that you have to clear (raid junk mobs - RJMs) that take 10 mins to kill and cannot hit the tank makes for 300 fucking boring minutes.  What part of this is fun or challenging?  No loot, no suspence, just AFK and and autofollow... STOP PUTTING SHIT LIKE THIS IN THE GAME.  Give raid mobs MORE power since the auto attack doesn't do shit and they are usually drained in 20 fucking seconds (good job Dave).  Take the hps down a notch since RJMs are just that, junk.  X4 shouldn't give them a right to have 4 million hps. X4 should mean it hits x4 more, x4 harder, x4 more power, not take x40 times longer to kill.  These raid mobs give me horrid flash backs of VT but take out ALL the risk of dying and add a smaller hit box.  Hi, please..... <br /><br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/Aten1.jpg" alt="" style="border:none;" /><br /><br /><br />Right, so this is usually where I post some uber loot we got.  I am going to miss a few people/loots but Grats to the following........<br /><br /><center><br />Kythik on a Vclaw, ring and something else.<br />Stella on some cap, bp and other shit.<br />Patho on fucking not going ld everytime we zone ... and some good shit.<br />Van on ring and other lewts.<br />Xminos on noobie junk since hez lzr!<br />Mysti on rings....... <br />Faille on neck, arms, boots, rings...loothoe<br />Sigon for lots of shit (arms, bracer, bp and more) <-- another loot hoe.<br />Nyco on cap and something else I dont remember.<br />Elkay on a dragon tooth!<br />Allora on having so much fucking power regen loot you can't cast enough to use it!!! LMAO.<br />Dave on whip and ring since you whine so much.<br />Insog on not getting shit in forever!<br />Every caster on getting 16/16 robes - Meomi, Eason, Aidem and Nyco!!<br />Mero on a ruby, boots, and plat robe.<br />Enda on Idol.<br />Aescu on uber leet ring from a dildo.<br />Miang on ring.<br />Euk on uber dps and some item :/<br />Ssinum on ?<br />Kienas on Ring of Removal.<br />Me on being pimped out by a fucking awesome crew and to gdam lazy to put links up of all this shit hahah!<br />Triton on becoming an Atrocity.../snicker  <br /><B>And finally grats everyone on having Prismatics!!!!</B></center><br /><br /><br />Ok ok so I have a new name for the quote section.  One member of the guild has been extremely vocal about wanting a quote section and continuous updates... so here it is....<br /><br /><B>STFU KYTHIK</B><br /><br /><br />Yak's obsession with bards<br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/yak2.JPG" alt="" style="border:none;" /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/yak1.JPG" alt="" style="border:none;" /><br /><br /><br />Mero and his hobbies.<br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/mero.JPG" alt="" style="border:none;" /><br /><br /><br />Exos and how he got to be leet.<br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/exos.JPG" alt="" style="border:none;" /><br /><br /><br />Euk's Wisdom.<br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/eukatae.JPG" alt="" style="border:none;" /><br /><br /><br />Elkay narrating Wild America.<br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/elkaywisdom.JPG" alt="" style="border:none;" /><br /><br /><br />Lunch Meat.<br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/Myst funny.JPG" alt="" style="border:none;" /><br /><br /><br />Bulk laughter.<br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/Myst Quotes Feb March.jpg" alt="" style="border:none;" /><br /><br /><br />Oh my.<br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/gmwarning.JPG" alt="" style="border:none;" /><br /><br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/ServersDown.JPG" alt="" style="border:none;" /><br /><br /><br />MYSTERY PICTURE:  If you can guess who this is, i'll give you 1 plat...nm I have no money due to 20gp repair costs.<br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/mypanties.JPG" alt="" style="border:none;" /><br /><br /><br />Adios<br />-Noah
		<p>  :: <a href="/eq2/index.php?action=fullnews&amp;showcomments=1&amp;id=13">Comments (0)</a> ::  
[<a href="#top">top</a>]</p>			
