      <tr>
        <td width="763" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#996666" class="box_links">
		<img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10018/normal_Darathar.jpg" alt="" style="border:none;" /border=0 width=700 height=525><br /><br /><br />What a great fight this was!!  People were at the top of their game on this fight and we took this bitch down 2.67 times.  2.67 times??   At some point Darathar thought it would be funny to go from 1% health to full health.  We wont talk about what happened on the .67 (/wink Elkay).<br /><br /><br /><A HREF="http://fohguild.org/eq2/forums/files/dara5_199.jpg"><img src=http://fohguild.org/eq2/forums/files/dara5_199.jpg border=0 width=700 height=525></A></center><br /><br /><br />Courtesy of our guild photographers (IE people that go LD during raids <3 ) you can sample <a href=http://fohguild.org/eq2/forums/viewtopic.php?t=97>more Darathar pics here.</a><br /><br /><br />As far as what else has been happening... killing x4s, epic zones, and trying out new strat like Templar MTanking (Photo coming soon!!).  Lots of loot so click <a href=http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/thumbnails.php?album=1>here</a> to see some of the new toys we have.  <br /><br /><br />-Noah Notfuror
